---
title: Smart AI Travel Agent — Sequence Diagram (plan + chat refinement)
config:
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Traveler
    participant SPA as React SPA<br/>(PlannerPage)
    participant Ctrl as TripsController
    participant Cur as ICurrentUserService<br/>(DemoCurrentUserService)
    participant Plan as TripPlanningService
    participant AI as IAiPlannerService<br/>(AzureOpenAiPlannerService)
    participant OAI as Azure OpenAI<br/>(gpt-4o 'planner')
    participant Val as ItineraryValidator
    participant Db as TravelAgentDbContext<br/>→ Azure SQL

    Traveler->>SPA: type "5 relaxed days in Lisbon…"
    SPA->>Ctrl: POST /api/trips/plan { request }
    Note over Ctrl: RateLimiter 'ai'<br/>10 req/min per IP
    Ctrl->>Cur: GetCurrentUserIdAsync()
    Cur->>Db: find-or-create demo user
    Db-->>Cur: userId
    Ctrl->>Plan: PlanAsync(userId, request)
    Plan->>Db: load TravelerPreference
    Db-->>Plan: preferences (budget, pace, interests…)
    Plan->>AI: GeneratePlanAsync(PlanningContext)
    AI->>OAI: CompleteChatAsync(system + user msgs,<br/>strict JSON schema 'itinerary')
    OAI-->>AI: itinerary JSON
    AI->>Val: Validate(draft)
    alt draft invalid
        AI->>OAI: re-prompt once with validation errors
        OAI-->>AI: corrected itinerary JSON
        AI->>Val: Validate(draft)
    end
    Val-->>AI: normalized draft (USD, day numbering, limits)
    AI-->>Plan: ItineraryDraft
    Plan->>Plan: derive day costs + trip total<br/>(never trusted from the model)
    Plan->>Db: save Trip + Days + Items<br/>+ user/assistant ChatMessages
    Db-->>Plan: persisted trip
    Plan-->>Ctrl: TripDetailDto
    Ctrl-->>SPA: 200 OK (itinerary + chat history)
    SPA-->>Traveler: render day cards + cost badges

    Traveler->>SPA: "make day 2 cheaper"
    SPA->>Ctrl: POST /api/trips/{id}/chat { message }
    Ctrl->>Plan: PlanAsync(userId, message, tripId)
    Plan->>Db: load trip + days + last 12 chat turns
    Db-->>Plan: current itinerary + history
    Plan->>AI: GeneratePlanAsync(context incl.<br/>current itinerary + history)
    AI->>OAI: CompleteChatAsync(…)
    OAI-->>AI: revised itinerary JSON
    AI-->>Plan: ItineraryDraft
    Plan->>Db: replace days, append chat turns
    Plan-->>Ctrl: TripDetailDto
    Ctrl-->>SPA: 200 OK (updated plan)
    SPA-->>Traveler: re-render itinerary
